00:02:06,410 --> 00:02:10,470
I knew it. Anyone who walks out from the imperial tomb alive

6
00:02:10,470 --> 00:02:12,620
is not an ordinary man.

7
00:02:13,700 --> 00:02:17,320
The Marquis of Pingjin is truly fortunate to have you,

8
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:19,990
a talented and experienced aide in politics working for him.

9
00:02:20,630 --> 00:02:22,080
You flatter me.

10
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:25,360
I've been his aide for only a few days.

11
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:27,800
I'm not good at socializing, but I appreciate your compliments.

12
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:31,030
Please get to the point.

13
00:02:31,030 --> 00:02:32,470
Fine.

14
00:02:32,470 --> 00:02:34,830
I'll get to the point.

15
00:02:36,190 --> 00:02:39,800
I'm Xiang Antu, the owner of Zhen Tower.

16
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:42,830
Greetings, Owner Xiang.

17
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:45,590
This is our third meeting.

18
00:02:45,590 --> 00:02:47,030
I really didn't expect this.

19
00:02:47,030 --> 00:02:50,280
You were penniless when you had just arrived at the capital

20
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:55,050
but you're now the Chief Aide for the Marquis of Pingjin.

21
00:02:55,050 --> 00:02:59,430
You were rapidly promoted in just a few months.

22
00:02:59,430 --> 00:03:01,150
I'm really curious.

23
00:03:01,150 --> 00:03:07,400
What tactics did you use to rise rapidly overnight?

24
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:11,320
I was merely lucky.

25
00:03:12,910 --> 00:03:14,280
Let me be frank.

26
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:16,190
I admire your talent.

27
00:03:16,190 --> 00:03:18,380
We've crossed paths more than once,

28
00:03:18,380 --> 00:03:20,520
and I consider that fate.

29
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,960
Since you can become the aide of the Marquis of Pingjin,

30
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:26,310
why not also consider becoming an honored guest of Zhen Tower?

31
00:03:26,310 --> 00:03:28,840
Be it wealth or fame,

32
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:33,160
I can give you whatever the Marquis gives you.

33
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:39,240
Are you trying to poach the aide of the Marquis?

34
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,630
Can't I do that?

35
00:03:40,630 --> 00:03:43,490
It's extremely worthwhile to be my friend.

36
00:03:48,310 --> 00:03:49,840
Forgive me.

37
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:53,430
If you think highly of me, I will remember this.

38
00:03:53,430 --> 00:03:55,710
As for being friends,

39
00:03:55,710 --> 00:03:57,950
I dare not social climb.

40
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:03,090
Previously, at Zhen Tower,

41
00:04:03,090 --> 00:04:06,900
Yang Zhen, Qu Jiao, and Chu Huaiming humiliated you.

42
00:04:06,900 --> 00:04:08,740
I could've just stood by and watched.

43
00:04:08,740 --> 00:04:11,630
Do you know why I helped you?

44
00:04:11,630 --> 00:04:13,560
It's because you're different from them.

45
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:17,120
You're not evil by nature.

46
00:04:18,380 --> 00:04:20,360
That's why you should know

47
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:22,430
the Marquis of Pingjin is a military general.

48
00:04:22,430 --> 00:04:26,190
He kills without hesitation and trusts no one.

49
00:04:26,190 --> 00:04:30,430
Working for him is like living your life on the edge.

50
00:04:30,430 --> 00:04:35,450
So, tell me, why seek connections with him and put your life at risk?

51
00:04:35,450 --> 00:04:37,020
You're a pearl covered in dust. 
  (Hidden talent) 

52
00:04:37,020 --> 00:04:39,030
I think it's a waste for you.

53
00:04:42,070 --> 00:04:44,310
You're too kind, Owner Xiang.

54
00:04:44,310 --> 00:04:47,970
I'm just a fake pearl passing off as a genuine pearl.

55
00:04:47,970 --> 00:04:51,840
Everything I did was just to survive in this vast world

56
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:54,710
and find a safe place to stay.

57
00:04:55,430 --> 00:04:58,800
This is what you said but I can see this is not your aspiration.

58
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:02,130
Are you trying to help him regain command of the army

59
00:05:02,130 --> 00:05:04,790
to prove your worth?

60
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:14,150
I always hope to do what others can't.

61
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:19,090
Looks like I was wrong about you.

62
00:05:19,090 --> 00:05:21,600
You and the Marquis are the same kind of people.

63
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,920
In that case, I won't force you again.

64
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:26,100
I wish you great success and glory.

65
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:28,360
Thank you, Owner Xiang.

66
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,930
I'll take my leave.

67
00:05:35,870 --> 00:05:37,380
Sir, please remember this.

68
00:05:37,380 --> 00:05:40,510
Here in the capital, you'll need Zhen Tower's help

69
00:05:40,510 --> 00:05:43,120
far more than I'll need yours.

70
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:45,510
If you're ever in trouble and look for me,

71
00:05:45,510 --> 00:05:49,270
remember what you said today and don't be embarrassed.

72
