00:09:31,650 --> 00:09:33,150
 - Thank you... 
 - Here you go. 

141
00:09:33,150 --> 00:09:34,600
What's going on?

142
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:36,750
- Someone's distributing porridge. 
  - Here, take this. 

143
00:09:36,750 --> 00:09:38,820
 - Thank you. 
 - The Marquis is so kind. 

144
00:09:38,820 --> 00:09:40,550
 - Come back if you need more. 
 - Thank you. 

145
00:09:40,550 --> 00:09:42,030
 Be careful, it's hot. Hold it properly. 

146
00:09:42,030 --> 00:09:43,520
 - Here.  
 - Thank you, sir.

147
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:44,520
 There's more if you need it. 

148
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:46,320
- Little girl, take this. 
 - Thank you.

149
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:49,240
- Be careful, it's hot. 
 - Thank you.

150
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:51,480
 Take this. 

151
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:53,200
Here.

152
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:55,320
 - Thank you. 
 - Thank you. 

153
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:57,830
 - Here. 
 - Thank you. 

154
00:09:59,020 --> 00:10:00,210
 Thank you. 

155
00:10:00,210 --> 00:10:01,480
 - Here, take this. 
 - Thank you. 

156
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:03,960
- Greetings, Marquis. 
  - The Marquis is so kind. 

157
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:06,300
 - Next.  
 - What are you doing?

158
00:10:06,300 --> 00:10:07,720
 - Be careful, it's hot. 
 - All right. 

159
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:11,440
Marquis, I received some reciprocal gifts yesterday.

160
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:15,130
It weighed heavily on me, so I converted the gifts into grains

161
00:10:15,130 --> 00:10:19,480
and gave them out in your name to the struggling commoners.

162
00:10:22,270 --> 00:10:23,840
The Marquis is here!

163
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:26,490
The Marquis is here!

164
00:10:26,490 --> 00:10:27,870
Thank you, Marquis, for your grace!

165
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:29,790
Thank you for your kindness!

166
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:32,600
 Thank you for your grace! 

167
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:37,670
 - We'll never forget your kindness. 
 - Thank you, My Lord! 

168
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:40,130
- All right, enough. 
  - Thank you for your grace! 

169
00:10:40,130 --> 00:10:44,270
The Marquis is giving out porridge for you to fill your stomachs.

170
00:10:44,270 --> 00:10:45,290
Go and get it.

171
00:10:45,290 --> 00:10:47,320
 Thank you, Marquis! 

172
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:49,480
 Thank you, Marquis! 

173
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,610
 Let's go and get the porridge! 

174
00:10:50,610 --> 00:10:53,000
 Let's go and get the porridge. Quick. 

175
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,200
 There's enough for everyone! 

176
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:56,150
I acted on my own.

177
00:10:56,150 --> 00:10:58,230
Please forgive me, Marquis.

178
00:11:00,910 --> 00:11:04,320
Zang Hai, I didn't expect you

179
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:07,010
to handle this beautifully. I underestimated you.

180
00:11:07,010 --> 00:11:08,490
 - That's enough. 
 - Thank you. 

181
00:11:08,490 --> 00:11:11,080
My Lord, I'm embarrassed.

182
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:13,670
I dare not forget that I'm serving you.

183
00:11:13,670 --> 00:11:16,000
Those gifts were too expensive and extravagant.

184
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,320
If I had accepted them,

185
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:20,480
I would have been indebted to them on your behalf.

186
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:24,950
By doing this today, I believe it'll stop them from sending gifts again.

187
00:11:24,950 --> 00:11:27,300
If they send them again, just accept the gifts.

188
00:11:27,300 --> 00:11:32,670
Do you think I can't eliminate disasters or solve problems for them?

189
00:11:32,670 --> 00:11:34,420
I dare not think this way.

190
00:11:34,420 --> 00:11:35,840
Once you're done distributing the porridge,

191
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:39,440
go to my study and retrieve "Wei Liaozi's Military Strategies".

192
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:42,110
If you follow me, don't just read the Four Books and Five Classics of Confucianism.

193
00:11:42,110 --> 00:11:44,700
Read more books on military strategies, too.

194
00:11:45,340 --> 00:11:46,750
Understood.

195
00:11:58,820 --> 00:12:00,580
Congratulations, Sir Zang!

196
00:12:01,180 --> 00:12:06,980
The Marquis just granted you access to his study. Consent is not required.

197
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:27,610
Tea tastes better when brewed in this jade teapot.

198
00:12:27,610 --> 00:12:29,360
If you like it, keep it.

199
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:31,300
There won't be any again in the future.

200
00:12:31,300 --> 00:12:34,360
Everyone in the capital knows about yesterday's incident.

201
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:37,150
No one will deliver gifts again today.

202
00:12:37,150 --> 00:12:40,270
Whether you accept them or not, it leads to trouble.

203
00:12:40,270 --> 00:12:43,910
Turn them down, and you'll seem arrogant and invite suspicion.

204
00:12:43,910 --> 00:12:45,720
But I can't just accept them either.

205
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:48,150
Yang Zhen served the Marquis for over a decade.

206
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:51,270
The Marquis knows him inside out.

207
00:12:51,270 --> 00:12:55,440
Yang Zhen can violate the taboo and accept gifts, but I can't.

208
00:12:55,440 --> 00:13:00,190
That's right. Many eyes are watching you now.

209
00:13:00,190 --> 00:13:04,720
However, you're quick to pick up on these matters.

210
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:07,280
I wonder who taught you these.

211
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:09,320
Of course, you taught me these.

212
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:13,850
Master, were you ever in officialdom?

213
00:13:13,850 --> 00:13:15,900
It's inexplicable.

214
00:13:15,900 --> 00:13:18,370
When I was making waves back then,

215
00:13:18,370 --> 00:13:21,080
you were still busy playing in the mud.

216
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:25,720
There's something I never expected.

217
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:28,630
The mastermind behind the famed Zhen Tower

218
00:13:28,630 --> 00:13:32,720
is actually that pretty young lady.

219
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:37,040
She set me up at first, but then pulled me out of danger.

220
00:13:37,040 --> 00:13:40,320
She now wants me to turn against the Marquis and join her.

221
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:44,890
She made you a generous offer and you even declined her.

222
00:13:44,890 --> 00:13:46,850
She's not a simple person.

223
00:13:47,540 --> 00:13:52,110
She's smart, resourceful, and doesn't seem like a bad person.

224
00:13:52,110 --> 00:13:55,720
Zang Hai really played this game beautifully.

225
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:59,480
All the poor people in the capital received his kindness.

226
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:02,910
Not only did he kill off the intentions of those who sent the gifts,

227
00:14:02,910 --> 00:14:05,850
he obtained recognition from the Marquis.

228
00:14:09,940 --> 00:14:11,700
You've been outsmarted.

229
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:23,970
Looking at your smile... Zang Hai will be facing bad luck.

230
00:14:23,970 --> 00:14:26,300
Do something for me.

231
00:14:26,300 --> 00:14:28,200
What are you up to again?

232
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:32,280
When news comes from Eighth Young Master, the entire capital believes it.

233
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:33,600
Spread a few words for me.

234
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:35,300
What are they?

235
00:14:35,300 --> 00:14:39,730
   

236
00:14:39,730 --> 00:14:40,870
No way.

237
00:14:40,870 --> 00:14:43,120
I only speak the truth. I don't start rumors.

238
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:44,680
You make your living off Zhen Tower

239
00:14:44,680 --> 00:14:45,610
and you still dare to decline me?

240
00:14:45,610 --> 00:14:47,120
Will you help me or not?

241
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:48,810
I'm not helping you.

242
00:14:50,050 --> 00:14:52,140
When you previously insisted on talking about the Empress Dowager,

243
00:14:52,140 --> 00:14:53,600
you drew the attention of the undercover guards.

244
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:56,040
Didn't I get you out of trouble?

245
00:14:56,600 --> 00:15:00,200
I did that to help Zhen Tower earn more money.

246
00:15:02,370 --> 00:15:03,390
How about this?

247
00:15:03,390 --> 00:15:06,630
You'll get extra cuts from ticket sales for your future storytelling sessions.

248
00:15:09,870 --> 00:15:12,030
Just help me this once. All right?

249
00:15:12,030 --> 00:15:15,340
I'm begging you. Please?

250
00:15:15,840 --> 00:15:18,020
Let's be clear. Just this once.

251
00:15:18,020 --> 00:15:19,670
Make it once a year.

252
00:15:19,670 --> 00:15:21,810
It's only once in this lifetime.

253
00:15:22,310 --> 00:15:25,340
The seawater overflows, drowning the strong tree.

254
00:15:25,340 --> 00:15:28,200
The tiger in the grass is bound to die.

255
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:31,200
Its claws, heart, and ears will decay.

256
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:34,360
Among ten thousand people, someone hides,

257
00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:37,360
bringing ruin to his master.

258
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:40,000
The seawater overflows, drowning the strong tree.

259
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:42,940
The tiger in the grass is bound to die.

