299
00:18:19,130 --> 00:18:21,640
I've provided every possible excuse.

300
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:24,510
A smart person will know how to slip away.

301
00:18:24,510 --> 00:18:29,930
But what if Zang Hai doesn't leave and loses his life instead?

302
00:18:29,930 --> 00:18:32,720
That's the price he pays for choosing the Marquis of Pingjin.

303
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:36,110
But I think he won't die that easily.

304
00:18:36,110 --> 00:18:38,520
