308
00:18:51,200 --> 00:18:54,380
Seems like someone still hasn't given up on trying to win your favor.

309
00:18:54,380 --> 00:18:56,590
All right, I know. You may leave.

310
00:18:56,590 --> 00:18:58,250
Understood.

311
00:19:23,020 --> 00:19:25,690
 "You moved into the Marquis Mansion with hidden motives." 

312
00:19:25,690 --> 00:19:26,780
 "I, too, have suffered at his hands." 

313
00:19:26,780 --> 00:19:28,400
 "I failed to take revenge." 

314
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:30,880
