320
00:26:43,830 --> 00:26:48,220
Father. Mother.

321
00:26:48,220 --> 00:26:50,650
Please watch over me.

322
00:26:50,650 --> 00:26:53,650
I must kill the Marquis of Pingjin.

323
00:26:53,650 --> 00:26:55,690
When it's done,

324
00:26:56,680 --> 00:26:59,690
I'll give you both a proper burial.

