00:28:28,590 --> 00:28:30,640
Zang Hai, have some, too.

327
00:28:30,640 --> 00:28:33,700
 The maids deliver refreshments every afternoon 

328
00:28:33,700 --> 00:28:36,100
 and dinner at You hour (5:00 - 7:00 p.m.) 

329
00:28:36,100 --> 00:28:38,590
 During this time, the steward is always present. 

330
00:28:38,590 --> 00:28:40,430
 There's no way to take action. 

331
00:28:41,030 --> 00:28:45,640
 Perhaps, the only opportunity is when I'm alone with the Marquis. 

332
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:47,700
 I'll poison him then. 

333
00:28:59,800 --> 00:29:01,670
Thank you. 
    

334
