335
00:29:15,930 --> 00:29:17,500
- They are fresh. 
 - Customers, take a look at the tea leaves.

336
00:29:17,500 --> 00:29:21,060
- Fresh fruit... Sweet and juicy! 
 - There are all kinds of tea leaves.

337
00:30:13,400 --> 00:30:16,000
You're awake.

338
00:30:20,300 --> 00:30:21,600
You're Hui Jian.

339
00:30:21,600 --> 00:30:23,930
I didn't expect you to remember me.

340
00:30:26,600 --> 00:30:28,400
You're the one who threatened me.

341
00:30:28,400 --> 00:30:31,280
When did I threaten you?

342
00:30:32,740 --> 00:30:35,720
Disciple, what is he talking about?

343
00:30:35,720 --> 00:30:37,110
No idea, Master.

344
00:30:37,110 --> 00:30:39,240
He's spouting nonsense.

345
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:41,880
Did you hit him too hard?

346
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:45,760
No way. I know how much force I used.

347
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:50,700
Who ordered you?

348
00:30:50,700 --> 00:30:52,600
Ordered us?

349
00:30:55,330 --> 00:30:59,300
Do you think we look like we would take orders?

350
00:30:59,300 --> 00:31:01,450
Why did you tie me up?

351
00:31:14,110 --> 00:31:15,920
I'll be honest.

352
00:31:15,920 --> 00:31:17,980
I need a favor from you.

353
00:31:17,980 --> 00:31:21,100
I want to borrow something. Your face.

354
00:31:22,650 --> 00:31:26,590
I want to slice it and wear it on my face.

355
00:31:26,590 --> 00:31:30,580
You want to use my face to impersonate me?

356
00:31:30,580 --> 00:31:32,080
That's right.

357
00:31:34,750 --> 00:31:36,720
The truth is,

358
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:39,300
I've been dormant in the Marquis Residence for many years

359
00:31:39,300 --> 00:31:42,200
just for one very important matter.

360
00:31:43,400 --> 00:31:45,500
It's to get close to the Marquis of Pingjin.

361
00:31:46,290 --> 00:31:49,780
When Yang Zhen left, I thought my opportunity finally came.

362
00:31:49,780 --> 00:31:52,210
No one else could stop me.

363
00:31:53,800 --> 00:31:58,600
I didn't expect you to show up and dismiss us.

364
00:32:00,260 --> 00:32:03,780
I lost my opportunity. I hate you.

365
00:32:04,940 --> 00:32:08,830
Did it occur to you that this face-switching won't work?

366
00:32:08,830 --> 00:32:10,110
This kind of far-fetched trick

367
00:32:10,110 --> 00:32:12,300
will fall apart once you set foot in the Marquis Residence.

368
00:32:12,300 --> 00:32:14,400
That's because you lack foresight.

369
00:32:14,400 --> 00:32:16,040
Don't worry.

370
00:32:17,210 --> 00:32:19,500
My knife skills are excellent. It won't hurt.

371
00:32:19,500 --> 00:32:22,900
And we'll give you a proper ritual to send you off.

372
00:32:22,900 --> 00:32:25,180
You're insane!

373
00:32:40,100 --> 00:32:43,900
In fact, I'm very sorry

374
00:32:43,900 --> 00:32:46,160
but I really don't have a choice.

375
00:32:46,160 --> 00:32:48,200
Don't worry, I won't live long after this.

376
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:51,770
I'll personally apologize to you in the netherworld.

377
00:32:55,070 --> 00:32:56,900
Shi Lei!

378
00:33:00,500 --> 00:33:02,070
Don't you know how to tie a man up?

379
00:33:02,070 --> 00:33:04,030
I tied him up tightly.

380
00:33:04,030 --> 00:33:06,400
This brat is strong.

381
00:33:06,400 --> 00:33:08,500
Come, hold him down.

382
00:33:10,610 --> 00:33:12,600
The Eight-Lancet Set?

383
00:33:12,600 --> 00:33:14,300
You're quite knowledgeable.

384
00:33:14,300 --> 00:33:15,690
Where did you get these tools?

385
00:33:15,690 --> 00:33:17,380
None of your business.

386
00:33:19,170 --> 00:33:20,400
Let me ask you.

387
00:33:20,400 --> 00:33:22,440
Why do you want to get close to the Marquis?

388
00:33:22,440 --> 00:33:24,100
You're going to die anyway.

389
00:33:24,100 --> 00:33:26,100
I might as well tell you.

390
00:33:26,100 --> 00:33:28,550
I want to get close to him

391
00:33:28,550 --> 00:33:31,900
so that I can kill him and avenge my master.

392
00:33:31,900 --> 00:33:33,500
Your master?

393
00:33:33,500 --> 00:33:35,830
Isn't he right here?

394
00:33:36,600 --> 00:33:38,900
He's not my real master.

395
00:33:38,900 --> 00:33:41,430
I'm avenging the death of my real master.

396
00:33:42,300 --> 00:33:45,200
Who are you referring to?

397
00:33:45,200 --> 00:33:47,540
Enough. Stop wasting time.

398
00:33:47,540 --> 00:33:49,810
In any case, you will die today.

399
00:33:52,480 --> 00:33:57,100
Yes. In any case, I'll die today. Let me finish talking.

400
00:33:57,100 --> 00:33:59,400
Even if you really want to use my face,

401
00:33:59,400 --> 00:34:04,140
taking the skin above the neck won't be sufficient.

402
00:34:04,140 --> 00:34:06,110
You didn't know this, right?

403
00:34:06,110 --> 00:34:09,880
The skin on the neck, chest and back are all connected.

404
00:34:09,880 --> 00:34:13,760
One mistake and you'll tear the whole thing.

405
00:34:13,760 --> 00:34:15,800
If you want a clean cut,

406
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:17,800
you need to start from the back.

407
00:34:17,800 --> 00:34:20,000
Cut the crap. I don't need you to tell me this.

408
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:23,210
Of course I know. I was just testing the angle.

409
00:34:24,500 --> 00:34:26,640
Strip him. Hurry.

410
00:34:34,360 --> 00:34:35,890
What's wrong?

411
00:34:36,720 --> 00:34:38,000
There are scars.

412
00:34:38,000 --> 00:34:39,630
So what?

413
00:34:39,630 --> 00:34:42,480
We just need his face.

414
00:34:43,800 --> 00:34:46,660
- I'll knock him out now. 
 - Wait!

415
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:49,580
How did you get these scars?

416
00:34:50,110 --> 00:34:55,230
I got them from being whipped as a child.

417
00:34:57,230 --> 00:34:59,550
My father was in Dongxia back then.

418
00:34:59,550 --> 00:35:02,400
My senior brother applied medicine for me.

419
00:35:02,400 --> 00:35:05,190
But the wounds were too deep. He couldn't do anything.

420
00:35:05,190 --> 00:35:09,290
Later, a master helped to patch up the scars for me.

421
00:35:09,290 --> 00:35:11,190
Why were the scars patched up?

422
00:35:11,190 --> 00:35:14,860
Because I also have a blood feud to settle.

423
00:35:29,760 --> 00:35:31,850
You are...

424
00:35:32,780 --> 00:35:35,070
When my senior brother was three years old,

425
00:35:35,070 --> 00:35:38,180
my father took him in as a disciple.

426
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:40,560
As kids, we would go up the mountains together

427
00:35:40,560 --> 00:35:42,760
to survey the land and gather herbs.

428
00:35:42,760 --> 00:35:45,410
We skipped lessons and were punished together.

429
00:35:45,410 --> 00:35:49,500
Whenever I got into trouble, I'd make him take the blame.

430
00:35:49,500 --> 00:35:51,730
I was always pranking him.

431
00:35:58,230 --> 00:36:00,180
Your senior brother...

432
00:36:01,490 --> 00:36:05,400
because he made a mistake, he was punished and sent to the back mountain.

433
00:36:06,030 --> 00:36:09,480
He couldn't die with his master and his wife...

434
00:36:11,000 --> 00:36:14,230
and has been barely surviving till today.

435
00:36:15,340 --> 00:36:17,690
Although he wasn't outstanding,

436
00:36:17,690 --> 00:36:21,500
he was the disciple my father doted on the most.

437
00:36:21,500 --> 00:36:26,790
If Father knew he were still alive, he would be overjoyed.

438
00:36:28,800 --> 00:36:31,590
Father named him Guan Feng*, 
  (*Watching the wind) 

439
00:36:31,590 --> 00:36:37,590
hoping he would live freely like the wind.

440
00:36:41,900 --> 00:36:43,890
I am Guan Feng.

441
00:36:46,070 --> 00:36:48,460
I am Guan Feng!

442
00:36:48,460 --> 00:36:52,480
I am Guan Feng! It's really you, Zhinu!

443
00:36:52,480 --> 00:36:55,060
You're alive!

444
00:36:55,060 --> 00:36:59,780
Zhinu... it's good that you're alive.

445
00:36:59,780 --> 00:37:02,080
It's good that you're alive.

446
00:37:17,180 --> 00:37:20,650
That's the whole story.

447
00:37:21,920 --> 00:37:24,900
So, your face was changed.

448
00:37:24,900 --> 00:37:27,560
No wonder I didn't recognize you.

449
00:37:28,510 --> 00:37:31,310
Weren't you also chubby back then?

450
00:37:35,230 --> 00:37:37,710
We've changed a lot.

451
00:37:46,380 --> 00:37:49,950
Is that young master of yours really reliable?

452
00:37:50,920 --> 00:37:52,870
He's an orphan from outside the capital.

453
00:37:52,870 --> 00:37:54,380
He's devoted to his training.

454
00:37:54,380 --> 00:37:56,010
We've known each other for years.

455
00:37:56,010 --> 00:37:59,400
Besides, he's willing to help me take revenge.

456
00:37:59,400 --> 00:38:01,280
Don't worry,

457
00:38:01,280 --> 00:38:05,510
but he's not my real master.

458
00:38:07,710 --> 00:38:11,570
Seems like you've also been through a lot over the past years.

459
00:38:12,550 --> 00:38:14,440
Tell me everything.

460
00:38:21,070 --> 00:38:24,020
That day, Master's wife sent me to the mountain

461
00:38:24,020 --> 00:38:26,520
to chop firewood and reflect on my mistakes.

462
00:38:28,510 --> 00:38:32,470
Just after nightfall, I saw Master returning from the southwest.

463
00:38:32,470 --> 00:38:36,050
I thought Master's wife would be glad to see him coming home...

464
00:38:36,050 --> 00:38:38,330
 - Master, Master!  
 - and wouldn't punish me.

465
00:38:38,330 --> 00:38:40,750
-  Master...  
 - So, I rushed down the mountain.

466
00:38:42,820 --> 00:38:46,290
But when I was almost home, I suddenly heard screams.

467
00:38:46,290 --> 00:38:47,940
A group of people were at the entrance

468
00:38:47,940 --> 00:38:49,630
and they were armed with swords.

469
00:38:49,630 --> 00:38:51,980
I hid right away.

470
00:38:54,400 --> 00:38:58,190
I saw someone come out from inside.

471
00:38:58,190 --> 00:39:00,280
It was the Marquis of Pingjin.

472
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:04,070
I later saw Master and his wife being carried out by his men.

473
00:39:04,070 --> 00:39:07,970
 I was terrified. I didn't know what had happened. 

474
00:39:07,970 --> 00:39:10,880
I waited till they'd left and ran home.

475
00:39:10,880 --> 00:39:13,030
But the fire had already spread. I couldn't get inside.

476
00:39:13,030 --> 00:39:15,510
 Help! Put out the fire immediately! 

477
00:39:15,510 --> 00:39:17,280
 Uncle Li, put out the fire quickly! 

478
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:19,800
I wanted to seek help from the neighbors

479
00:39:19,800 --> 00:39:23,810
but when I opened the door, that place was full of corpses.

480
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:39,880
After that, I ended up on the streets,

481
00:39:39,880 --> 00:39:42,860
living from day to day.

482
00:39:42,860 --> 00:39:44,200
But all this time,

483
00:39:44,200 --> 00:39:47,590
I held on to the Eight-Lancet Set Master gave me,

484
00:39:47,590 --> 00:39:51,310
and vowed to take revenge one day.

485
00:39:53,970 --> 00:39:56,510
 - Two buns, please. 
 - Right away. 

486
00:39:59,400 --> 00:40:01,850
 - Here you go. 
 - Thank you. 

487
00:40:26,630 --> 00:40:28,580
 - Sir. 
 - Coming! 

488
00:40:28,580 --> 00:40:29,510
 Here's the money for the bun. 

489
00:40:29,510 --> 00:40:31,570
 All right. Thank you. 

490
00:40:32,190 --> 00:40:33,360
 Go ahead and eat. 

491
00:40:33,360 --> 00:40:36,880
That day, I met Shi Lei and Kaizhen Sanren.

492
00:40:36,880 --> 00:40:41,060
They took me in and Shi Lei became my new master.

493
00:40:42,480 --> 00:40:45,230
After Kaizhen Sanren passed away from illness,

494
00:40:45,230 --> 00:40:48,340
Shi Lei and I depended on each other for survival.

495
00:40:49,670 --> 00:40:54,400
But there's one thing I've never let go of.

496
00:40:54,400 --> 00:40:56,180
That is revenge.

497
00:40:56,180 --> 00:40:57,660
So, later,

498
00:40:57,660 --> 00:41:01,590
I thought of a way to enter the Marquis Residence as an aide.

499
00:41:01,590 --> 00:41:03,560
It's my fault.

500
00:41:03,560 --> 00:41:08,170
I was incompetent. All these years, and I still couldn't get close to him.

501
00:41:08,170 --> 00:41:11,800
But fortunately, you're here now.

502
00:41:11,800 --> 00:41:13,880
Let's take revenge together.

503
00:41:14,670 --> 00:41:17,280
You're now the Chief Aide of the Marquis.

504
00:41:17,280 --> 00:41:20,040
How should we make it convenient for you to take action?

505
00:41:21,400 --> 00:41:24,910
Actually, before you two came, someone tried to force me to kill the Marquis.

506
00:41:24,910 --> 00:41:30,140
I was about to take the risk but you both captured me.

507
00:41:31,230 --> 00:41:33,110
You said that person threatened you.

508
00:41:33,110 --> 00:41:34,960
Who could he be?

509
00:41:37,280 --> 00:41:39,110
I'm not sure yet

510
00:41:39,110 --> 00:41:42,000
but it's not important who he is.

511
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:44,690
I'm going to kill the Marquis of Pingjin anyway.

512
00:41:47,360 --> 00:41:51,330
You just mentioned there's something crucial. What is it?

513
00:41:51,330 --> 00:41:54,000
The Marquis of Pingjin killed many people in our family

514
00:41:54,000 --> 00:41:57,690
because he was after something my father brought back from Dongxia.

515
00:41:57,690 --> 00:41:59,360
But he didn't succeed.

516
00:41:59,360 --> 00:42:02,480
Father must have hidden it beforehand

517
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:06,360
but I can't figure out where he could've hidden it.

518
00:42:09,590 --> 00:42:11,790
Something was hidden?

519
00:42:12,940 --> 00:42:15,730
He hid something?

520
00:42:15,730 --> 00:42:18,810
Didn't you just say that when my father returned from Dongxia,

521
00:42:18,810 --> 00:42:20,690
he came from the southwest?

522
00:42:21,400 --> 00:42:23,880
Normally, he should've come from the northeast.

523
00:42:23,880 --> 00:42:27,670
If he came from the southwest, he would have taken a detour.

